
# fix: Bug fixes → PATCH version
# feat: New features → MINOR version
# feat!: Breaking changes → MAJOR version
# perf: Performance improvements
# refactor: Potential improvements suggested by linters
# style: Cosmetic changes suggested by formatters
# docs: Documentation
# test: Tests
# build: Build configurations and external dependencies
# ci: Continuous integration
# chore: Miscellaneous changes

# <type>(<scope>)!: <subject> [ci skip]
#
# BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
# Closes/Fixes/Resolves #0
